{"id": 1844, "genre": 1000, "title": "在当下，你觉得人们对“安全感”的误解都体现在哪些事上？", "description": "如今的年轻人是不是活得都太小心了？", "record_count": 12889, "comment_count": 51, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201708101650343ocGLCkEst80yBAS.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-13T17:00:54Z", "questions": [{"id": 2778, "title": "在当下，你觉得人们对“安全感”的误解都体现在哪些事上？", "content": "你觉得现实生活中，人们对“安全感”的误解都体现在哪些事上？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 228411, "content": "“拒绝新技术总是安全的”，对AI、转基因总有被迫害妄想", "image": "img/option/option/20170810002413ElQ9f8qz7hogna6w.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228412, "content": "束缚、控制自己的伴侣和家人，让对方离开自己的成本变高", "image": "img/option/option/20170810002452b49mvoAGBURsfMtN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228413, "content": "公开场合谨慎表达自己，“不能乱说，当心被请去喝茶”", "image": "img/option/option/20170810045652vfC9jRezn1N6Q5rI.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228414, "content": "看待事物有自我审查滤镜：“这种尺度的片子竟然能过审？”“查水表！”", "image": "img/option/option/201708100034417sZoG9KnQwqHeg2C.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228415, "content": "为了自己的稳定安全，不分青红皂白地排挤外地人、移民、难民", "image": "img/option/option/2017081000263163iw0tlFPradZqj7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228416, "content": "一边老觉得别人“辱华”，一边自我陶醉看不上其他国家/民族", "image": "img/option/option/20170810044046Em3pBzZOGd8SPf25.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228417, "content": "从职业规划到个人提升，首要考虑的是稳定，恐惧变化", "image": "img/option/option/20170810042953f3k9iYm5G0URvStu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228418, "content": "在意别人的看法，希望被关注、认同、点赞，否则觉得自己不够好", "image": "img/option/option/20170810044644YfZkoatLvuy5JzSP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228419, "content": "迷信权威，发表观点总希望有靠谱的人背书，否则自己不敢这么说", "image": "img/option/option/201708100458024fTKANWsPdYay7Lq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228420, "content": "执行社会期望角色，比如到年纪就该结婚，男生要有个男人样等", "image": "img/option/option/20170810045525DCWbFh2wpEd7Ynz3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}